    "name": "Iso Racer",
    "steam_appid": 2234020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/9cdb16c9a8e2ef254b29aa035f25d3b4.avif?t=1711471425\" width=600 height=149 /></span><br>在《Iso Racer》中，玩家控制各种赛车，在不同赛道上参加一系列赛事。该游戏具有多人游戏模式，允许玩家与人工智能或其他玩家在线竞争。游戏的物理效果也很逼真，与漂移相结合，使游戏变得更加有趣。玩家可以定制自己的车辆并提高其性能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>漂流风格</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/efea8f11dce95bcbf61f39463963b5d3.poster.avif?t=1711471425\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/efea8f11dce95bcbf61f39463963b5d3.webm?t=1711471425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/efea8f11dce95bcbf61f39463963b5d3.mp4?t=1711471425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏的开始很简单，它看起来像一个典型的自上而下的赛车游戏，但不要让它欺骗你！你需要在弯道前适当降低速度，才能以完美的漂移通过弯道！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>汽车损坏只是视觉上的</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/bcd8602625710b66935b47a382dacf9d.poster.avif?t=1711471425\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/bcd8602625710b66935b47a382dacf9d.webm?t=1711471425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/bcd8602625710b66935b47a382dacf9d.mp4?t=1711471425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Iso Racer是一款由Pogo Concepts开发并发行的赛车游戏。该游戏具有自上而下的视角，深受经典赛车游戏的启发，同时仍然提供在线多人游戏等现代功能。<br><br>我们也关心玩家之间的互动，这就是为什么我们决定以车辆上方的云的形式进行聊天，并且我们计划在未来添加更多类型的比赛，超出同一时间的标准比赛游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/a545fc0476a2081a0ae9634e124ff9a1.poster.avif?t=1711471425\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/a545fc0476a2081a0ae9634e124ff9a1.webm?t=1711471425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234020/extras/a545fc0476a2081a0ae9634e124ff9a1.mp4?t=1711471425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>总体而言，Iso Racing 提供了既有趣又富有挑战性的赛车体验，既怀旧又现代。它对策略和定制的重视使其有别于其他街机风格的赛车游戏，其在线多人游戏模式为那些希望与世界各地的其他玩家竞争的人提供了无尽的可重玩性。",
